# Privacy Policy

**Last Updated:** November 21, 2025

## Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how Platform Title Generator ("we," "our," or "the App") handles your information when you use our iOS application. Your privacy is important to us, and we're committed to being transparent about how we collect and use your data.

## What Information Do We Collect?

### Information You Provide
- **Videos**: When you generate titles, you select videos from your device. These videos are sent to our AI service temporarily to create titles.
- **Generated Titles**: The titles we create for you are saved on your device so you can access them later.
- **Preferences**: Your choices for platforms (YouTube Shorts, Instagram Reels, TikTok) and languages are saved on your device.

### Information Stored on Your Device
- **Coin Balance**: Your coin balance is stored securely on your device.
- **Purchase History**: Information about your in-app purchases is handled by Apple and stored according to their privacy policies.

## How Do We Use Your Information?

### Title Generation
- When you generate titles, your video is sent to our AI service to analyze the content and create optimized titles.
- Videos are processed temporarily and are **not stored** on our servers or by the AI service. They are deleted immediately after processing.

### Data Storage
- All generated titles are stored **only on your device**.
- Your coin balance is stored securely on your device.
- We don't store your videos or personal information on our servers.

### In-App Purchases
- Purchases are processed through Apple's App Store.
- We only use purchase information to deliver the coins you've purchased.

### Advertising
- The App shows optional rewarded advertisements.
- Watching ads is completely optional - you choose when to watch them to earn coins.
- You can control ad tracking through your device's privacy settings.

## Third-Party Services

### AI Service (Google Gemini)
- **What**: Your videos are sent to Google's AI service to generate titles
- **Why**: To analyze your video content and create optimized titles
- **Storage**: Videos are **not stored** - they're processed and immediately deleted
- **Privacy**: [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

### Ad Service (Google AdMob)
- **What**: Displays optional rewarded advertisements
- **Why**: To allow you to earn coins by watching ads
- **Privacy**: [Google AdMob Privacy Policy](https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543)

### Apple Services
- Purchases are processed through Apple's App Store
- Your data is subject to [Apple's Privacy Policy](https://www.apple.com/privacy/)

## How Is Your Data Protected?

- **Local Storage**: All your data is stored on your device, not on our servers
- **Secure Storage**: Your coin balance is stored using Apple's secure storage system
- **Encrypted Transmission**: All data sent to our services uses secure encryption
- **No Video Storage**: We never store your videos - they're processed and deleted immediately

## Your Rights

### Access and Control
- You can view all your generated titles in the App
- You can delete any title or all titles at any time
- You can copy titles directly from the App

### Your Choices
- Watching ads is completely optional
- You can control ad tracking in your device settings
- You can delete all your data by deleting the App

### Data Deletion
- To delete all your data, simply delete the App from your device
- All titles and preferences will be removed

## Data Retention

- **Generated Titles**: Stored on your device until you delete them
- **Videos**: Never stored - deleted immediately after processing
- **Coin Balance**: Stored on your device
- **Purchase History**: Managed by Apple according to their policies

## Children's Privacy

This App is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with information, please contact us immediately.

## International Data Transfers

When you use the App, your videos may be processed in data centers located in different countries. All data transfers comply with applicable privacy laws and use appropriate security measures.

## Your Privacy Rights

Depending on where you live, you may have additional rights:

- **Access**: Request access to your personal data
- **Deletion**: Request deletion of your data
- **Correction**: Request correction of inaccurate data
- **Objection**: Object to certain types of data processing

To exercise these rights, please contact us using the information below.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make changes, we'll update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. For significant changes, we may notify you through the App.

We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

